46:32.869 --> 46:34.827
♪ I don't know go,
I don't know go, girl ♪

46:34.911 --> 46:37.869
♪ Go girl, go girl,
gotta go girl ♪

46:37.952 --> 46:39.243
♪ You won, babe... ♪

