Automated Voice:
Subject disconnected.

46:47.077 --> 46:48.827
Subjected disconnected.

46:48.911 --> 46:51.952
-(gasps)
-Subject disconnected.

46:52.035 --> 46:54.577
-Subject disconnected.
-(slow, deep breathing)

46:54.661 --> 46:57.369
-Subject disconnected.
