46:57.452 --> 46:59.160
Subject disconnected.

47:00.243 --> 47:02.202
-(ringing stops)
-Subject disconnected.

47:02.993 --> 47:05.118
Subject disconnected.

47:05.202 --> 47:07.744
Subject disconnected.

47:15.202 --> 47:16.285
(beeps)

47:23.661 --> 47:24.577
(beeps)

48:19.993 --> 48:22.744
-(chimes)
-(speaking Spanish)

48:27.202 --> 48:28.494
(chimes)

48:41.535 --> 48:44.285
-(chimes)
-(speaking Arabic)

48:45.452 --> 48:46.952
(chimes)

48:55.993 --> 48:57.786
-(chimes)
-Blake: I don't know
why I keep coming

48:57.869 --> 49:01.202
to these stupid phone booths
and telling you jokes.

49:02.410 --> 49:03.744
(sighs)

49:03.827 --> 49:06.993
It's not like you ever
had a sense of humor.

49:07.077 --> 49:10.243
I know you're probably never
gonna hear this anyway.

49:10.327 --> 49:12.993
Sometimes, it's...

49:13.077 --> 49:15.744
Sometimes it's nice to pretend.

49:16.869 --> 49:18.202
(chimes)

49:26.202 --> 49:29.369
So many prayers
unanswered.

49:30.911 --> 49:32.452
I own and operate
thousands

49:32.535 --> 49:35.285
of Manhattan booths
around the world.

49:35.952 --> 49:39.285
You wouldn't believe
what people ask him for.

49:39.661 --> 49:43.369
They beg and beg
and beg for his help.

49:44.619 --> 49:46.786
Beg for him to come
down from the heavens

49:46.869 --> 49:48.869
and make things better.

49:49.619 --> 49:52.535
But he ignores them,
every single one.

49:54.202 --> 49:55.535
Do you know why?

49:57.410 --> 49:58.827
I give up.

49:58.911 --> 50:01.619
Because Dr. Manhattan
isn't listening.

50:02.535 --> 50:04.202
He's not even on Mars.

50:04.702 --> 50:06.577
Where is he?

50:07.202 --> 50:09.202
Right here in Tulsa,

50:09.786 --> 50:11.369
pretending to be human.

50:14.035 --> 50:16.786
Are you the one who put that
idea in my grandfather's head?

50:16.869 --> 50:19.577
Actually,
he put it in mine.

50:21.911 --> 50:23.577
Angela...

50:26.035 --> 50:28.744
are we going to keep
fucking around here?

50:29.869 --> 50:32.577
Or are we going to be
honest with each other?

50:33.869 --> 50:35.494
Tell me how you
know my grandfather,

50:35.577 --> 50:37.369
and tell me what the fuck
you're doing here,

50:37.452 --> 50:39.786
and don't say it's
saving fucking humanity.

50:39.869 --> 50:42.661
Your grandfather came to me
because he needed someone

50:42.744 --> 50:44.827
with my resources to help him

50:44.911 --> 50:47.077
stop the 7th Kavalry.

50:47.993 --> 50:50.494
Stop them from doing what?

50:50.577 --> 50:52.577
In less than
an hour,

50:52.661 --> 50:55.077
they're going to capture
Dr. Manhattan,

50:55.160 --> 50:57.702
and they're going
to destroy him.

50:58.118 --> 51:01.619
And then, they're
going to become him.

51:03.619 --> 51:06.535
Can you imagine
that kind of power

51:06.619 --> 51:09.619
in the hands of
white supremacists?

51:10.535 --> 51:12.993
I'm sorry, Angela. I know
you asked me not to say it,

51:13.077 --> 51:16.285
but I am saving
fucking humanity.

51:18.452 --> 51:20.202
I'm leaving now

51:20.285 --> 51:23.118
'cause that's the craziest
shit I've ever heard.

51:24.202 --> 51:25.827
Okay.

51:30.869 --> 51:33.619
You didn't ask me
who he is.

51:35.827 --> 51:39.369
-What?
-I know you think
I'm crazy, but...

51:41.327 --> 51:43.702
I just told you
Dr. Manhattan is here,

51:43.786 --> 51:46.911
in Tulsa, walking amongst
us as a human being,

51:46.993 --> 51:49.369
and you never
asked me who he is.

51:53.786 --> 51:54.952
(beeps)

52:02.952 --> 52:04.993
Why you
always hungry?

52:05.077 --> 52:07.410
Fast metabolism.

52:11.744 --> 52:13.993
I'm gonna go
check this out.

52:18.619 --> 52:20.827
(tires screech, motor revving)

52:29.786 --> 52:32.911
-Tell Scare to move.
-No, he's not gonna move.

52:32.993 --> 52:34.327
And you're under arrest.

52:34.410 --> 52:35.744
Jen,

52:35.827 --> 52:38.494
tell Scare to move.
I don't want to hurt him.

52:40.661 --> 52:42.952
It's Abar!
She wants you to move!

52:43.035 --> 52:44.827
She says she doesn't
want to hurt you!

52:44.911 --> 52:46.911
Red Scare:
Fuck her!

52:47.494 --> 52:49.619
Did you tell her
she's under arrest?!

52:51.744 --> 52:55.035
-(tires screech)
-You crazy fucking bitch!

52:57.452 --> 52:59.243
(Pirate Jenny shouts
indistinctly)

53:02.744 --> 53:04.410
Fuck you!

53:07.494 --> 53:09.619
(tires screech)

53:30.661 --> 53:33.786
(clattering)

54:00.285 --> 54:01.911
Angela?

54:02.661 --> 54:05.077
Are the kids asleep?

54:05.160 --> 54:07.077
Yeah.

54:07.160 --> 54:09.619
-You okay?
-I'm fine.

54:10.452 --> 54:12.369
I don't understand. What
happened? I came to see you,

54:12.452 --> 54:15.786
-but they wouldn't let me--
-Cal, I need you to stop talking

54:15.869 --> 54:17.535
and listen to me, okay?

54:18.077 --> 54:19.452
Okay.

54:19.535 --> 54:22.035
You're a great husband,

54:22.827 --> 54:24.993
an amazing father,

54:26.786 --> 54:29.619
you're the best friend
I've ever had.

54:30.494 --> 54:32.285
I love you.

54:33.035 --> 54:34.494
I love you, too.

54:35.827 --> 54:37.993
(clattering)

54:43.661 --> 54:46.202
Time to come out
of the tunnel.

54:50.160 --> 54:51.744
What, uh...

54:52.702 --> 54:54.869
-tunnel?
-Don't be scared.

54:55.535 --> 54:57.827
We talked about this.

54:58.369 --> 55:00.619
We always knew that
this day would come.

55:00.702 --> 55:04.160
-What day, Angela? I don't know
what you're talking about--
-You do know.

55:05.494 --> 55:07.993
You just don't remember.

55:08.993 --> 55:11.827
Did we talk about this
before my accident?

55:13.827 --> 55:16.077
There was no accident.

55:17.202 --> 55:18.410
What?

55:18.494 --> 55:20.369
It was a lie.

55:20.869 --> 55:23.577
A lie so that
we could be together.

55:24.786 --> 55:26.702
At least for a while.

55:29.869 --> 55:33.619
If it's any consolation,
it was your idea.

55:35.077 --> 55:36.243
Honey,

55:36.327 --> 55:38.452
I don't know what...

55:39.243 --> 55:40.202
they did to you,

55:40.285 --> 55:42.661
but I think
the drug you took

55:42.744 --> 55:45.410
is messing you up.

55:46.619 --> 55:48.369
You're not yourself.

55:49.160 --> 55:51.494
No, Jon.

55:51.577 --> 55:54.285
You're not yourself.

55:56.577 --> 55:58.744
My name is not Jon.

55:58.827 --> 56:01.077
I am so sorry.

56:01.452 --> 56:03.369
(grunts)

56:09.911 --> 56:11.577
(grunts)

56:18.285 --> 56:19.661
(hammer clatters)

56:30.035 --> 56:32.619
(sighs)

56:41.285 --> 56:43.243
Hey, baby.

56:44.911 --> 56:47.619
We're in fucking trouble.

59:05.452 --> 59:07.452
♪ (SLOW JINGLE PLAYS) ♪

59:10.911 --> 59:13.118
-MAN: I love you.
-ANGELA ABAR: We just met.

59:13.619 --> 59:14.702
When'd you fall in love with me?

59:14.786 --> 59:17.577
MAN: I...
was already in love with you.

59:17.661 --> 59:19.118
ANGELA: Before you even saw me?

59:19.494 --> 59:23.744
MAN: I don't experience
the concept of... before.

59:24.285 --> 59:26.118
So... there's no moment?

59:26.577 --> 59:28.452
-MAN: Moment?
-A moment.

59:28.952 --> 59:31.452
When you realized,
"I'm in love."

59:35.786 --> 59:37.077
MAN: This is the moment.

59:39.202 --> 59:41.202
I just told you that
you can't save me.

59:44.285 --> 59:46.160
And you're gonna try to
anyway.

59:46.577 --> 59:48.202
♪ (MUSIC CONCLUDES) ♪
